item.title: Features
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row section="yes"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Built in drag’n’drop Visual Composer

We have adjusted and incorporated Visual Composer plugin into our theme. You can easily build unlimited number of layout, because you can visualize what you will get at site page in the process of creation. Also it is very easy to rearrange and edit already created layouts.

[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="invisible" icon="star"][vc_single_image img_size="full" image="1257" animate="afc" align="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section="yes" background="alternate"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Extensive Style Options

Astra theme comes with 8 predefined color schemes. But you can go beyond them - adjust one of predefined or create your very own color scheme! Every color on the page can be changed.

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image img_size="full" image="1257" animate="afc" align="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section="yes"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Retina Ready and Fully Responsive

Astra theme provides responsive and flexible design. All page layouts works perfectly on all devices, from large monitors to mobile phones. All elements enhanced for Retina displays, so they look clean and sharp on modern gadgets.

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image img_size="full" image="1257" animate="afc" align="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section="yes" img="1259" parallax="yes" parallax_speed="slow" parallax_reverse="yes" background="primary"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Parallax Effect Sections

You can easuly add 3D looking parallax backgrounds to page sections. Change Parallax Effect speed and even make it reversed.

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image img_size="full" image="1257" animate="afb" align="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section="yes"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Advanced Layout Options. Unlimited Sidebars

The theme gives you opportunity to change layout settings for whole site and for each particular page. One common Sidebar is not enough for you? You can easily create unlimited number of Sidebars and add different Widgets there to fit your needs on every page.

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image img_size="full" image="1257" animate="wfc" align="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section="yes" background="primary"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Over 249 Icons Integrated

Astra comes with entire FontAwesome Icons set integrated. You can use them at IconBoxes, Tabs, Accordions and many other cases.

[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="invisible" icon="star"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][vc_separator type="invisible" icon="star"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section="yes"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Quick Install and Demo Content Import

Astra is ready to use from the box. Quickly install it via FTP or WordPress and after you activate it you can load demo content in just One Button Click. Then you can add your own content on already designed pages.

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image img_size="full" image="1257" animate="afc" align="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section="yes"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Translation Ready. WPML Optimized

Astra is created with best translation practices in mind and already contains language po/mo files for easier translation. You can add/edit languages easily. In case you need to run multiple languages at once, the theme is optimized for the WPML plugin.

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image img_size="full" image="1257" animate="afb" align="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section="yes"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Revolution Slider Included

We have not only included this plugin into theme files, but also adjusted it’s style so you can create slides that will correspond overall Astra theme design. You can create unlimited number of Sliders with help of this Premium Plugin.

[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image img_size="full" image="1257" animate="afc" align="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section="yes"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Outstanding and Prompt Free Support

We care about our customers and provide 100% free lifetime support and updates. Answer customers` questions, guide and help them is number one priority for our team. You don’t have to take our word on it - see ratings of all our items at ThemeForest.
